lead_paragraph: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger used to dream about Luis Suarez, the signing that got away, and he will be hoping the Uruguayan striker doesn't give him nightmares when holders Barcelona visit in the Champions League on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal Must Keep Suarez Quiet, Says Wary Wenger
headline.main: Arsenal Must Keep Suarez Quiet, Says Wary Wenger
